{
  "texts": [
    "Most of the trackers cannot meet realtime tracking requirements.",
    "Trackers based on the improved CF framework (OTR [7], DMKCF [50], CCF [83], WCO [53], and TACF [51]), are constrained by their own speed.",
    "Two real-time trackers (DSKCF [49] and DSOH [46]) have the original CF architecture.",
    "The transformer-based tracker SPT, also achieves favorable performance and real-time speed.",
    "Experimental comparison of RGB-T datasetsWe selected 19 trackers as our baseline to perform an overall comparison of the GTOT and RGBT234 datasets."
  ]
}